tion-prompt\"></p>\n        <div class=\"choices\" id=\"prediction-choices\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"step phenomenon\" id=\"observe\" aria-labelledby=\"observe-title\">\n      <p class=\"step-number\">2</p>\n      <div class=\"stage\">\n        <h2 id=\"observe-title\"></h2>\n        <canvas id=\"simulation\" width=\"720\" height=\"400\" role=\"img\" aria-describedby=\"state-description\"></canvas>\n        <p id=\"state-description\" class=\"state\" aria-live=\"polite\"></p>\n        <div class=\"control-row\">\n          <label for=\"primary-control\" id=\"primary-label\"></label>\n          <input id=\"primary-control\" type=\"range\" disabled>\n          <output id=\"primary-output\" for=\"primary-control\" dir=\"auto\"></output>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"actions\">\n          <button id=\"reset\" type=\"button\"></button>\n          <button id=\"replay\" type=\"button\"></button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"step\" id=\"explain\" aria-labelledby=\"explain-title\" hidden>\n      <p class=\"step-number\">3</p>\n      <div>\n        <h2 id=\"explain-title\"></h2>\n        <p id=\"explanation-prompt\"></p>\n        <p id=\"misconception\" class=\"misconception\"></p>\n        <p id=\"transfer\"></p>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"runtime-error\" role=\"alert\" hidden>\n      <h2 id=\"runtime-error-title\"></h2>\n      <p id=\"runtime-error-copy\"></p>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n  <script>window.__LAYSH_LESSON__ = {\"safe\":true,\"unsafe_category\":null,\"simulatable\":true,\"reason_code\":\"safe_science_education\",\"lang\":\"ar\",\"canonical_intent\":\"investigate_resistance_effect_on_current_and_lamp_brightness_at_constant_voltage\",\"domain\":\"physics_electric_circuits\",\"title\":\"تأثير المقاومة في التيار وسطوع المصباح\",\"tldr\":\"عند جهد ثابت مقداره 6 V، تؤدي زيادة المقاومة R إلى انخفاض شدة التيار I والقدرة P، ولذلك يخفت المصباح. نفترض مصدرًا مثاليًا ومقاومة أومية، ونمثّل السطوع بالقدرة المتبددة.\",\"key_formula\":\"I = V / R؛ P = V² / R\",\"learning_objective\":\"أن يستنتج المتعلم سببيًا أن زيادة المقاومة عند ثبات الجهد تقلل شدة التيار والقدرة المتبددة، فتخفض سطوع المصباح.\",\"primary_parameter\":{\"id\":\"resistance_ohm\",\"label\":\"المقاومة\",\"unit\":\"Ω\",\"min\":2,\"max\":20,\"default\":6,\"step\":1},\"secondary_parameter\":null,\"prediction\":{\"prompt\":\"إذا تضاعفت المقاومة مع ثبات الجهد، فماذا يحدث للتيار وسطوع المصباح؟\",\"choices\":[\"ينخفض التيار ويخفت المصباح\",\"يزداد التيار ويزداد السطوع\",\"يبقى التيار والسطوع ثابتين\"]},\"misconception\":\"زيادة المقاومة تسمح بمرور تيار أكبر.\",\"explanation_prompt\":\"فسّر لماذا يخفت المصباح عندما تزداد المقاومة، مستعينًا بعلاقة المقاومة بكل من التيار والقدرة.\",\"transfer_prompt\":\"تنبّأ بما يحدث لتيار الدارة وسطوع المصباح عند استبدال مقاومة مقدارها 4 Ω بأخرى مقدارها 8 Ω مع بقاء الجهد ثابتًا.\",\"module_spec\":{\"outputs\":[\"current_a\",\"power_w\"]},\"checks\":[{\"id\":\"current_at_2_ohm\",\"kind\":\"numeric\",\"inputs\":[{\"name\":\"resistance_ohm\",\"value\":2}],\"output\":\"current_a\",\"expected\":3,\"tolerance\":0.01,\"unit\":\"A\"},{\"id\":\"power_at_2_ohm\",\"kind\":\"numeric\",\"inputs\":[{\"name\":\"resistance_ohm\",\"value\":2}],\"output\":\"power_w\",\"expected\":18,\"tolerance\":0.02,\"unit\":\"W\"},{\"id\":\"current_at_6_ohm\",\"kind\":\"numeric\",\"inputs\":[{\"name\":\"resistance_ohm\",\"value\":6}],\"output\":\"current_a\",\"expected\":1,\"tolerance\":0.01,\"unit\":\"A\"},{\"id\":\"power_at_6_ohm\",\"kind\":\"numeric\",\"inputs\":[{\"name\":\"resistance_ohm\",\"value\":6}],\"output\":\"power_w\",\"expected\":6,\"tolerance\":0.02,\"unit\":\"W\"},{\"id\":\"current_at_12_ohm\",\"kind\":\"numeric\",\"inputs\":[{\"name\":\"resistance_ohm\",\"value\":12}],\"output\":\"current_a\",\"expected\":0.5,\"tolerance\":0.01,\"unit\":\"A\"},{\"id\":\"power_at_12_ohm\",\"kind\":\"numeric\",\"inputs\":[{\"name\":\"resistance_ohm\",\"value\":12}],\"output\":\"power_w\",\"expected\":3,\"tolerance\":0.02,\"unit\":\"W\"}],\"suggestions\":[\"استكشف تأثير تغيير الجهد في شدة التيار.\",\"قارن القدرة المتبددة في مقاومتين مختلفتين.\",\"اختبر العلاقة بين المقاومة والطاقة المستهلكة خلال زمن محدد.\"]};</script>\n  <script>(() => {\n  \"use strict\";\n  const required = [\"destroy\", \"init\", \"resize\", \"setParameter\", \"test\", \"version\"];\n\n  window.LayshContract = Object.freeze({\n    assertSimulation(simulation) {\n      if (!simulation || typeof simulation !== \"object\") throw new Error(\"SIM_CONTRACT_MISSING\");\n      const keys = Object.keys(simulation).sort();\n      if (JSON.stringify(keys) !== JSON.stringify(required)) throw new Error(\"SIM_CONTRACT_KEYS\");\n      if (simulation.version !== 1) throw new Error(\"SIM_CONTRACT_VERSION\");\n      for (const method of [\"init\", \"setParameter\", \"test\", \"resize\", \"destroy\"]) {\n        if (typeof simulation[method] !== \"function\") throw new Error(\"SIM_CONTRACT_METHOD\");\n      }\n      return simulation;\n    },\n  });\n})();\n\n</script>\n  <script>window.LayshSimulation = (function () {\n  'use strict';\n\n  var canvas = null;\n  var context = null;\n  var width = 300;\n  var height = 360;\n  var locale = 'ar';\n  var emitFrame = null;\n  var resistance = 6;\n  var voltage = 6;\n\n  function finiteNumber(value, fallback) {\n    var number = Number(value);\n    return isFinite(number) ? number : fallback;\n  }\n\n  function clampResistance(value) {\n    return Math.max(2, Math.min(20, finiteNumber(value, 6)));\n  }\n\n  function calculate(value) {\n    return {\n      current_a: voltage / value,\n      power_w: voltage * voltage / value\n    };\n  }\n\n  function format(value, digits) {\n    return Number(value.toFixed(digits)).toString();\n  }\n\n  function isArabic() {\n    return typeof locale === 'string' && locale.toLowerCase().slice(0, 2) === 'ar';\n  }\n\n  function write(label, x, y, size, color, align) {\n    if (!context || typeof context.fillText !== 'function') return;\n    context.fillStyle = color;\n    context.font = '600 ' + size + 'px sans-serif';\n    context.textAlign = align || 'center';\n    context.textBaseline = 'middle';\n    context.fillText(label, x, y);\n  }\n\n  function strokeLine(x1, y1, x2, y2) {\n    if (!context || typeof context.beginPath !== 'function' ||\n        typeof context.moveTo !== 'function' || typeof context.lineTo !== 'function' ||\n        typeof context.stroke !== 'function') return;\n    context.beginPath();\n    context.moveTo(x1, y1);\n    context.lineTo(x2, y2);\n    context.stroke();\n  }\n\n  function drawBulb(x, y, radius, power) {\n    if (!context || typeof context.beginPath !== 'function' ||\n        typeof context.arc !== 'function' || typeof context.fill !== 'function') return;\n    var brightness = Math.max(0.17, Math.min(1, power / 18));\n    context.fillStyle = 'rgba(255, 193, 45, ' + (0.25 + brightness * 0.75) + ')';\n    context.strokeStyle = '#805817';\n    context.lineWidth = 2;\n    context.beginPath();\n    context.arc(x, y, radius, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n    context.fill();\n    if (typeof context.stroke === 'function') context.stroke();\n    context.fillStyle = '#697586';\n    if (typeof context.fillRect === 'function') {\n      context.fillRect(x - radius * 0.42, y + radius * 0.75, radius * 0.84, radius * 0.5);\n    }\n  }\n\n  function draw() {\n    if (!canvas || !context) return;\n    if (typeof context.clearRect !== 'function' || typeof context.fillRect !== 'function') return;\n\n    var w = Math.max(260, finiteNumber(width, finiteNumber(canvas.width, 300)));\n    var h = Math.max(300, finiteNumber(height, finiteNumber(canvas.height, 360)));\n    var surfaceW = Math.max(1, finiteNumber(canvas.width, w));\n    var surfaceH = Math.max(1, finiteNumber(canvas.height, h));\n    var canTransform = typeof context.save === 'function' &&\n      typeof context.restore === 'function' && typeof context.scale === 'function';\n\n    context.clearRect(0, 0, surfaceW, surfaceH);\n    if (canTransform) {\n      context.save();\n      context.scale(surfaceW / w, surfaceH / h);\n    }\n\n    context.fillStyle = '#eef5fb';\n    context.fillRect(0, 0, w, h);\n\n    var arabic = isArabic();\n    var result = calculate(resistance);\n    var pad = Math.max(14, w * 0.04);\n    var panelTop = 56;\n    var panelBottom = Math.min(h - 105, 260);\n    var left = pad + 20;\n    var right = w - pad - 20;\n    var topWire = panelTop + 62;\n    var bottomWire = panelBottom - 38;\n    var resistorX = left + (right - left) * 0.52;\n    var bulbX = left + (right - left) * 0.82;\n    var bulbY = (topWire + bottomWire) / 2;\n    var bulbRadius = Math.max(20, Math.min(30, (bottomWire - topWire) * 0.28));\n\n    write(arabic ? 'تأثير المقاومة في سطوع المصباح' : 'Resistance and lamp brightness', w / 2, 28, w < 520 ? 18 : 22, '#172b4d');\n\n    context.fillStyle = '#ffffff';\n    context.fillRect(pad, panelTop, w - pad * 2, panelBottom - panelTop);\n\n    context.strokeStyle = '#315b7d';\n    context.lineWidth = 3;\n    strokeLine(left, topWire, resistorX - 42, topWire);\n    strokeLine(resistorX + 42, topWire, bulbX, topWire);\n    strokeLine(bulbX, topWire, bulbX, bulbY - bulbRadius);\n    strokeLine(bulbX, bulbY + bulbRadius * 1.3, bulbX, bottomWire);\n    strokeLine(bulbX, bottomWire, left, bottomWire);\n    strokeLine(left, bottomWire, left, topWire);\n\n    context.strokeStyle = '#263b50';\n    context.lineWidth = 3;\n    if (typeof context.beginPath === 'function' && typeof context.moveTo === 'function' &&\n        typeof context.lineTo === 'function' && typeof context.stroke === 'function') {\n      context.beginPath();\n      context.moveTo(resistorX - 42, topWire);\n      var segment;\n      for (segment = 0; segment < 7; segment += 1) {\n        context.lineTo(resistorX - 30 + segment * 10, topWire + (segment % 2 === 0 ? -9 : 9));\n      }\n      context.lineTo(resistorX + 42, topWire);\n      context.stroke();\n    }\n    write('R = ' + format(resistance, 1) + ' Ω', resistorX, topWire - 25, 14, '#263b50');\n\n    var batteryX = left + (right - left) * 0.15;\n    strokeLine(batteryX - 8, bottomWire - 13, batteryX - 8, bottomWire + 13);\n    context.lineWidth = 5;\n    strokeLine(batteryX + 8, bottomWire - 21, batteryX + 8, bottomWire + 21);\n    write('6 V', batteryX, bottomWire + 34, 14, '#263b50');\n\n    drawBulb(bulbX, bulbY, bulbRadius, result.power_w);\n\n    var cardsY = panelBottom + 12;\n    var cardsH = Math.max(70, h - cardsY - 12);\n    var gap = 10;\n    var cardW = (w - pad * 2 - gap) / 2;\n    var labels = arabic ? ['شدة التيار', 'القدرة (مؤشر السطوع)'] : ['Current', 'Power (brightness)'];\n    var displayed = [format(result.current_a, 2) + ' A', format(result.power_w, 2) + ' W'];\n    var colors = ['#087f73', '#b86000'];\n    var index;\n    for (index = 0; index < 2; index += 1) {\n      var cardX = pad + index * (cardW + gap);\n      context.fillStyle = '#ffffff';\n      context.fillRect(cardX, cardsY, cardW, cardsH);\n      write(labels[index], cardX + cardW / 2, cardsY + cardsH * 0.32, w < 520 ? 12 : 14, '#4b5f73');\n      write(displayed[index], cardX + cardW / 2, cardsY + cardsH * 0.68, w < 520 ? 19 : 23, colors[index]);\n    }\n\n    if (canTransform) context.restore();\n  }\n\n  function safeDraw() {\n    try {\n      draw();\n    } catch (error) {\n      return;\n    }\n  }\n\n  function signalFrame() {\n    if (typeof emitFrame === 'function') emitFrame();\n  }\n\n  return {\n    version: 1,\n    init: function (options) {\n      options = options || {};\n      canvas = options.canvas || null;\n      context = options.context || null;\n      if (!context && canvas && typeof canvas.getContext === 'function') {\n        try {\n          context = canvas.getContext('2d');\n        } catch (error) {\n          context = null;\n        }\n      }\n      width = finiteNumber(options.width, canvas ? finiteNumber(canvas.width, 300) : 300);\n      height = finiteNumber(options.height, canvas ? finiteNumber(canvas.height, 360) : 360);\n      locale = options.locale || 'ar';\n      emitFrame = options.emitFrame;\n      resistance = 6;\n      safeDraw();\n      signalFrame();\n    },\n    setParameter: function (name, value) {\n      if (name === 'resistance_ohm') resistance = clampResistance(value);\n      safeDraw();\n      signalFrame();\n    },\n    test: function (inputs) {\n      var value = 6;\n      var index;\n      if (Array.isArray(inputs)) {\n        for (index = 0; index < inputs.length; index += 1) {\n          if (inputs[index] && inputs[index].name === 'resistance_ohm') {\n            value = clampResistance(inputs[index].value);\n          }\n        }\n      } else if (inputs && inputs.resistance_ohm !== undefined) {\n        value = clampResistance(inputs.resistance_ohm);\n      }\n      return calculate(value);\n    },\n    resize: function (newWidth, newHeight) {\n      width = finiteNumber(newWidth, width);\n      height = finiteNumber(newHeight, height);\n      safeDraw();\n      signalFrame();\n    },\n    destroy: function () {\n      canvas = null;\n      context = null;\n      emitFrame = null;\n    }\n  };\n}());</script>\n  <script>(() => {\n  \"use strict\";\n  const lesson = window.__LAYSH_LESSON__;\n  const dir = document.documentElement.dir;\n  const ar = lesson.lang === \"ar\";\n  const labels = ar\n    ? {\n        lesson: \"الجواب التفاعلي\",\n        predict: \"توقّع أولًا\",\n        observe: \"لاحظ ما يتغيّر\",\n        explain: \"فسّر ما رأيت\",\n        reset: \"إعادة الضبط\",\n        replay: \"إعادة العرض\",\n        runtimeTitle: \"تعذّر تشغيل المحاكاة\",\n        runtimeCopy: \"يمكنك الاحتفاظ بالجواب والمحاولة مرة أخرى من Laysh.\",\n      }\n    : {\n        lesson: \"Interactive answer\",\n        predict: \"Predict first\",\n        observe: \"Observe what changes\",\n        explain: \"Explain what you saw\",\n        reset: \"Reset\",\n        replay: \"Replay\",\n        runtimeTitle: \"The sim